format/theme/syntax-highlighting.md
     1→# Syntax highlighting
     2→
     3→mdBook uses [Highlight.js](https://highlightjs.org) with a custom theme
     4→for syntax highlighting.
    17→## Supported languages
    18→
    19→These languages are supported by default, but you can add more by supplying
